&\quad + \frac{A/m}{\left( \omega_0^2 - \omega^2 \right)^2 + \left( \frac{\gamma \omega}{m} \right)^2} \left[ \left( \omega_0^2 - \omega^2 \right) \cos(\omega t) + \frac{\gamma \omega}{m} \sin(\omega t) \right],
\end{align*}

for some constants $C_1$ and $C_2$. Differentiating twice with respect to time yields:

